--------------------------------------------------
BUSINESS RULES
--------------------------------------------------

• Customers may only view RFQs belonging to their approved company.
• Public RFQs must not expose internal data.
• Every update must create a history record.
• Soft delete only.
• Validate all status transitions.
• Never trust IDs from the frontend.
• Prevent IDOR attacks.
• Use optimistic concurrency.
• Use pagination for listing APIs.
• Support searching and filtering.
• Use DTOs for requests and responses.

